{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627750/extras/hr.png?t=1728739092\" /><br><br>First seize the power in your own country!<br><br>O.A.C is working hard to inspire their genre and make itself even better in the grand strategy game category.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627750/extras/anm.gif?t=1728739092\" /><br>Even if you're not exactly a human being...<br><br>Each country has its own internal dynamic, political structure, socio-economical order, and culture. Religions, ethnic groups, professions, NGOs, country problems, epidemics, natural disasters, economies and many more characteristics are determined within each country. Amid all this, create your own strategy to seize power in your country as a seemingly ordinary person.<br><br><strong>The Great War - AFTER THE OLD GOVERNMENT</strong><br><br>If you win the power struggle, you are at the start of your O.A.C journey. Changing technologies in all countries of the world brought along the nano-technological war. While the countries of the world were creating larger economies with each passing day, small countries were just bait waiting to be swallowed in a dead end.<br><br>You determine your task in the system you are in! All your decisions and the paths you will choose will affect your destiny first, then your nations, and ultimately the destiny of all humanity.<br><br><strong>THE APOCALYPTIC PERIOD</strong><br><br>Rich and futuristic story...<br><br>From different civilizations living outside the &quot;Known World&quot; to secret World organizations, the discovery of secrets hidden between the past and the future, from the existence of humanity to the present, is waiting for you. Being a strong leader on the stage of history heading towards an apocalyptic era will allow you to determine the living conditions of all humanity.<br><br>Remember, there will always be